title: US warship USS Hue City arrives in Klaipėda
text:
US warship USS Hue City arrives in Klaipėda BNS EN Monday, February 6, 2017 USS Hue City guided-missile cruiser of the United States Navy arrived in the Lithuanian port city of Klaipėda on Monday and docked in the port. USA flag © AP / Scanpix 
"The main objective of the visit is to strengthen ties with Lithuania and other NATO Allies, as well as ensure peace and stability in the Baltic region ," the US Embassy to Lithuania said on Facebook. 
The visit of the US warship was not announced in advance. 
Ieva Labanauskienė of the embassy told BNS that the crew of the vessel would stay in Lithuania for about a week, meeting with troops of the Lithuanian Navy , visiting Lithuanian warships and taking part in social projects. 122 Shared Why was there a purge of Russian Black Sea fleet commanders? (0) Ten high-ranking Russian intelligence and naval officers in Kaliningrad were fired over the last few weeks. Some believe the Kremlin took these drastic measures because of the fleet’s audacious actions that have put the West on edge, but others see more strategic reasons behind the move.
